1
00:01:30,930 --> 00:01:34,979
[The Lost National Treasure]

2
00:01:35,009 --> 00:01:37,789
[Episode 36]

3
00:01:39,229 --> 00:01:40,430
Give me back my child.

4
00:01:42,650 --> 00:01:43,200
Wen Wen,

5
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,800
this child is mine too.

6
00:01:46,070 --> 00:01:47,930
What did you promise me back then?

7
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,870
You said that no matter whose child he is,

8
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:51,729
once he's born,

9
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,590
he belongs to Yuanguang and me.

10
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:54,640
If I give you the child,

11
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,640
how will you raise him?

12
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,150
How will you provide for him?

13
00:01:57,150 --> 00:01:57,610
Wen Wen,

14
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,560
this isn't a path to life;

15
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:00,650
it's a path to ruin.

16
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,280
If Guang knew about this in the afterlife,

17
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,280
how could he ever rest in peace?

18
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,080
How dare you bring up Yuanguang?

19
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,440
If it hadn't been for you,

20
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:09,669
would he have ended up like this?

21
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,470
You ruined him.

22
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,760
You destroyed our whole family.

23
00:02:17,810 --> 00:02:20,460
I'll bear your hatred and resentment,
whatever it may be.

24
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:22,120
But I won't give you the child.

25
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,150
With me,

26
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,120
he can go to the best schools,

27
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,850
get the best education,

28
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,990
eat well and dress well.

29
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:31,950
Can you give him that?

30
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:35,030
The mistakes were ours.

31
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:36,910
He didn't do anything wrong.

32
00:02:36,910 --> 00:02:40,370
Why should we take away his chance
to grow up healthy and happy?

33
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,000
Wen Wen,

34
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,800
I'm doing this for your own good too.

35
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:45,190
The past is behind us.

36
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:46,970
Why not move on and look ahead?

37
00:02:47,210 --> 00:02:48,340
You're still young.

38
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:49,980
How will you ever remarry
if you're raising a child on your own?

39
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:52,640
Whether I remarry or not
is none of your concern.

40
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,600
That child is my flesh and blood.

41
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,329
I don't care whose blood

42
00:02:56,450 --> 00:02:58,010
runs in his veins anymore.

43
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:01,310
Even if we have to beg on the streets,

44
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:04,280
at least it's earned
with a clear conscience.

45
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,310
Unlike you,

46
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,030
every cent you earn

47
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,280
is stained with Yuanguang's blood.

48
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,260
If you're set on taking the child,

49
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,710
then sue me.

50
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,470
You were Guang's wife,

51
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:33,480
and I've always wanted the best for you.

52
00:03:34,460 --> 00:03:36,120
But when it comes to the child,

53
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,710
I won't give in.

54
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,630
It's alright now.

55
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:00,990
Let's cut the cake for the child.

56
00:04:02,650 --> 00:04:04,050
I don't know you anymore.

57
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:09,840
Today,

58
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,680
we're

59
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:14,520
joined by colleagues
from both the Public Security Bureau

60
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,320
and the Cultural Relics Bureau.

61
00:04:17,430 --> 00:04:19,490
A special welcome to Chief Cheng Zhi,

62
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,720
who just returned from Beijing

63
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,980
and came straight here from the airport.

64
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,090
Chief Cheng,

65
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:26,870
would you like to say a few words?

66
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:27,530
Chief Zhao,

67
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,980
I'm in no rush to speak.

68
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,750
Let's first hear what our colleagues

69
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,680
from both departments have to say.

70
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:41,960
Since no one is speaking up,
I'll go first.

71
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:45,020
The Uncle's gang

72
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:47,830
has been operating in Qinzhou Province

73
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:48,830
for over a decade.

74
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,650
Their criminal operations

75
00:04:51,190 --> 00:04:52,750
have persisted over a long period

76
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:54,680
and extended across a wide region.

77
00:04:54,710 --> 00:04:57,440
The gang members
come from diverse backgrounds,

78
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,870
ranging from ordinary citizens

79
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,390
to

80
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:03,000
prominent figures.

81
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,160
Honestly, I'm not one

82
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:07,240
to complain,

83
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,190
but today, I have to speak up.

84
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:12,100
We're really struggling.

85
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,560
We're facing three major challenges
in our investigations:

86
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,720
First, the number of cases
is overwhelming—

87
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,380
it's tough.

88
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,170
Second, there are too many
cultural relics to recover—

89
00:05:19,170 --> 00:05:19,620
that's tough too.

90
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:20,950
Third, there are many people to arrest—

91
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:21,880
again, not easy.

92
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,750
When these difficulties pile up,
it gets harder to handle.

93
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:24,190
These three—

94
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:25,120
Hold on a moment.

95
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:28,430
I know what you're trying to say,

96
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,650
so let me
put your mind at ease first, alright?

97
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,330
The March 17th case

98
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:39,040
has drawn significant attention
from leadership

99
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:41,570
at both
the provincial and municipal levels.

100
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:44,510
After much deliberation,
the provincial authorities have decided

101
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,920
to elevate the March 17th case

102
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,630
to a provincially supervised case.

103
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:51,830
The special investigation team
will be upgraded,

104
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:54,120
with the city bureau
assigning top officers

105
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,950
to reinforce the investigation team.

106
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:58,000
This also places higher demands

107
00:05:58,310 --> 00:05:59,570
on our investigators.

108
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:03,160
We must further refine
the division of responsibilities,

109
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,920
assigning specific individuals
to handle tasks

110
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:08,310
such as arrests, interrogations,

111
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,920
field investigations,
and case documentation

112
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,190
to improve overall efficiency.

113
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:12,250
If that's the case,

114
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:14,090
I won't say anything further.

115
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:16,920
While we're not afraid of challenges,

116
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,120
we certainly welcome

117
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,870
any support

118
00:06:20,190 --> 00:06:21,650
the leadership can offer.

119
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,160
Enough.

120
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:28,070
I know what you're getting at.

121
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:30,540
You're asking for

122
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:32,550
logistical support, right?

123
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:33,870
Rest assured,

124
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,800
the higher-ups have specifically
reviewed the matter

125
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,600
and issued clear instructions:

126
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,720
Funding for the investigation
will be fully guaranteed.

127
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,600
Necessary vehicles will be provided.

128
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,480
No matter which jurisdiction
the investigation leads to,

129
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,270
local police departments

130
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:49,000
are required to offer
full and unwavering support.

131
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,000
Thank you, sir.

132
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:56,120
There's a buzzword
making the rounds these days—"so dope."

133
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,510
Since our colleagues
at the Public Security Bureau

134
00:06:58,510 --> 00:07:00,480
have taken such a strong lead,

135
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,750
we at the Cultural Relics Bureau
can't drop the ball either.

136
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,480
During my recent trip to Beijing,

137
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:07,240
I met with leaders and experts from the
National Cultural Heritage Administration

138
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,160
and reported the details
of the March 17th case

139
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,800
to them.

140
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:12,190
The leaders specifically asked me

141
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:14,190
to convey their appreciation
for all your hard work.

142
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:16,600
They also hope you'll conduct a thorough
investigation into the criminal gang

143
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,480
and ensure it is completely dismantled.

144
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,560
Efforts to recover the involved
cultural relics must be intensified,

145
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:23,000
and we must prevent
any further loss of cultural heritage.

146
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,600
Of course,

147
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,120
our cultural relics department

148
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,850
will provide full cooperation

149
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:29,190
and coordinate closely
throughout the process.

150
00:07:29,190 --> 00:07:29,790
Comrades,

151
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,190
since the 18th National Congress,

152
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:33,830
the Central Committee has made

153
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:35,830
the protection of cultural relics
a top priority like never before.

154
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:38,270
issuing a series
of significant directives.

155
00:07:38,270 --> 00:07:40,240
The Ministry of Public Security and the
National Cultural Heritage Administration

156
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,510
have jointly established

157
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:44,000
a dedicated coordination group to combat
crimes related to cultural relics.

158
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:47,120
This group is tasked with deploying
efforts to crack down on such crimes,

159
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:49,800
overseeing major cases,

160
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:53,090
coordinating
cross-regional investigations,

161
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:56,159
and supporting local authorities
in safeguarding cultural heritage.

162
00:07:56,159 --> 00:07:57,070
At the same time,

163
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:58,990
we're gradually improving
the system and mechanism

164
00:07:58,990 --> 00:08:01,120
for recovering
cultural relics lost overseas,

165
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:03,120
ensuring their prompt return home.

166
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,800
On this basis,

167
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,930
commissioned by
Ministry of Public Security

168
00:08:06,930 --> 00:08:09,120
and
National Cultural Heritage Administration,

169
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:11,160
the Qinzhou Provincial
Public Security Department

170
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:14,560
has set up a national center
to combat cultural relic crimes.

171
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:17,070
The center has successfully completed
its trial operation

172
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,930
and will officially launch soon.

173
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:20,480
It will be responsible for

174
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,190
the collection, review,
analysis, and evaluation

175
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:25,310
of nationwide data
related to cultural relics crimes,

176
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,950
providing comprehensive
information support

177
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:29,010
to aid your efforts in solving cases.

178
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,400
Comrades,

179
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:35,750
our work in protecting cultural relics

180
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,669
has entered a new era.

181
00:08:38,419 --> 00:08:40,909
From the Central Committee
to the general public,

182
00:08:40,909 --> 00:08:42,970
everyone is paying close attention.

183
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,750
With that comes
even greater responsibility

184
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,720
on our shoulders.

185
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,250
However,

186
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,440
our confidence

187
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,270
has also grown stronger.

188
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:51,790
Folks,

189
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:54,650
let's just roll up our sleeves
and get to work!

190
00:08:58,370 --> 00:09:02,740
[Qinchuan Relics Inspection Team]
[Qinchuan Cultural Heritage Bureau]

191
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:08,080
Welcome!

192
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,510
Hurry up!

193
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,510
Thank you for coming.

194
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:12,270
Welcome.

195
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:13,630
-Welcome.
-Okay.

196
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:25,000
Any updates on
Liu Shusheng's construction company?

197
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:28,370
His accountant fled south

198
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:31,330
but has been apprehended
by our counterparts there.

199
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:33,440
Keep digging into the bank records.

200
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,620
Wu and Scar have been located.

201
00:11:06,890 --> 00:11:07,560
Police!

202
00:11:07,990 --> 00:11:08,520
Let's go.

203
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:22,230
Take him away.

204
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:33,390
Now, let me brief everyone
on the latest developments.

205
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:36,000
We've uncovered a new lead.

206
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,790
Recently,

207
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:39,030
Chief Wu

208
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:43,420
traveled to Xiao Guoqiang's hometown,
Huang Plain,

209
00:11:43,790 --> 00:11:46,790
and found out that, twenty years ago,
he worked as a driver for someone.

210
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:47,450
That person

211
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:49,930
was none other than

212
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:51,150
Zhao Youlin.

213
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:57,750
We looked into his background before.

214
00:11:58,470 --> 00:12:01,150
Didn't seem like he had any ties
to Huang Plain, right?

215
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:01,550
He did.

216
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:03,360
There was a connection.

217
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:06,230
Back then, Zhao Youlin had taken on
a construction project in Huang Plain.

218
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:08,270
During our investigation,
we heard some rumors

219
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,120
that

220
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:11,720
he uncovered an antique at the site.

221
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:13,150
Then he sold it off

222
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:15,280
and suddenly got rich overnight.

223
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:18,160
The story hasn't been confirmed,

224
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:19,550
but the fact

225
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:22,610
that Zhao Youlin deliberately
hid this part of his past

226
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:25,150
makes him very suspicious.

227
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:26,080
So,

228
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,080
we'll keep tracking Xiao Guoqiang.

229
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,180
As for Zhao Youlin,

230
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,960
look into him thoroughly.

231
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,560
Be careful. Watch your step.

232
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,530
This way.

233
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,100
Mind your head.

234
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:45,560
Director.

235
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,120
Director Zhang.

236
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,320
-Mrs. Zan.
-Thank you.

237
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,690
This is the section of

238
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:51,920
the rammed earth wall we've uncovered.

239
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,140
Shilin, take this.

240
00:12:55,850 --> 00:12:56,480
Look here.

241
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:58,790
Yes.

242
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,000
That's right.

243
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,300
Come on.

244
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:03,890
Director Zhang.

245
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:04,420
Mrs. Zan.

246
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,380
It is indeed a rammed earth wall.

247
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:12,690
Incredible.

248
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:14,150
Just incredible.

249
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,030
I heard

250
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,320
it's been quite the challenge

251
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,440
for your team
to find this rammed earth wall.

252
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,700
Don't even mention it.

253
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,720
Most archaeologists

254
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,390
look for signs of disturbed soil
in raw earth,

255
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:24,390
but we're out here

256
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,860
trying to find disturbed soil
inside disturbed soil,

257
00:13:25,860 --> 00:13:28,210
and rammed earth hidden in
more rammed earth.

258
00:13:28,210 --> 00:13:29,330
The terrain here

259
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,550
was originally uneven.

260
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:32,650
So, in the past,
when building the mausoleum complex,

261
00:13:32,650 --> 00:13:35,270
they first filled low areas,
then built rammed earth walls on top.

262
00:13:35,270 --> 00:13:36,470
As a result, we're now

263
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:38,670
searching for rammed earth
within rammed earth.

264
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,120
We've documented

265
00:13:40,630 --> 00:13:42,720
the number of boreholes
in our archaeological log,

266
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,520
but honestly,

267
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:45,360
if you asked us now,

268
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,340
we couldn't even tell.

269
00:13:46,340 --> 00:13:47,550
There are just too many.

270
00:13:47,550 --> 00:13:48,270
Sometimes,

271
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:50,790
we'd find two or three meters
of this rammed earth wall,

272
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:51,870
and then it would suddenly cut off.

273
00:13:51,870 --> 00:13:52,670
It's fragmented,

274
00:13:52,670 --> 00:13:54,200
with many twists and turns.

275
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:56,240
We've found traces of this kind of wall
surrounding the Yin Village grand tomb

276
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:59,150
in all four directions:
east, south, west, and north.

277
00:13:59,150 --> 00:14:00,440
Based on our preliminary estimates,

278
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,900
the remaining foundation

279
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,080
stretches about

280
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:05,040
1,200 meters from east to west,

281
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,650
and 860 meters from north to south,

282
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:09,670
forming a perfect enclosure
around both the Yin Village grand tomb

283
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:11,550
and the Dou Mausoleum.

284
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,120
Do you all remember

285
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:15,430
the paved stone remains
we discovered earlier?

286
00:14:15,430 --> 00:14:17,000
During this excavation,

287
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,480
we've uncovered several more sections.

288
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:21,030
At present, we estimate the structure
to be about 423 meters in length

289
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:22,360
and 1.5 meters in width.

290
00:14:22,570 --> 00:14:23,360
We believe

291
00:14:23,510 --> 00:14:24,510
this may mark

292
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:26,750
the boundary of the mausoleum complex
of the Yin Village grand tomb,

293
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:29,750
so we've tentatively named it
the "stone enclosure."

294
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:34,440
If that's the case,

295
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,050
then the Yin Village grand tomb

296
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:40,150
appears to have had
a stone-built mausoleum boundary.

297
00:14:40,150 --> 00:14:40,480
Yes.

298
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,170
The Dou Mausoleum

299
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:44,730
also has its own
rammed earth enclosure wall.

300
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:48,550
So both of them are located
within a single large mausoleum complex,

301
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:49,080
right?

302
00:14:49,130 --> 00:14:49,550
Yes.

303
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:52,870
This setup

304
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:55,160
clearly follows the burial tradition

305
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,670
where the emperor and empress share
a mausoleum but rest in separate tombs.

306
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:58,200
Exactly.

307
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,360
The configuration
of the Yin Village grand tomb

308
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,960
and the Dou Mausoleum

309
00:15:01,980 --> 00:15:04,240
is very similar to
the Yang Mausoleum of Han.

310
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:06,380
Therefore, we can basically confirm that

311
00:15:06,380 --> 00:15:08,720
we have found key evidence identifying

312
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:10,200
the Yin Village grand tomb

313
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,730
as the Zi Mausoleum
of Emperor Taizong of Han.

314
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:14,550
That's great.

